data.description: Enjoy life so-close to the water with no HOA in this updated charmer circa 1992 in popular Carrollwood Manor!  With close proximity to Marinas, Waterside Parks, fun waterfront restaurants and the Baltimore City Fire  Academy, you can vacation at home and be convenient to work and school.  The surroundings are great and the house does not disappoint.  Fenced front and rear yards lead to terrific spaces within.  Updated vinyl plank flooring on entire main and lower levels offer stylish easy maintenance and  a modern uniform look.  Fresh neutral paint on all three levels + terrific updates make the spaces feel light and brand new.  Open concept living & dining  spaces feature recent French Door with integral blinds leading to trex deck and an elevated view of the friendly neighborhood.  Efficient eat-in Kitchen with updated stainless appliances and pantry.  Upper level is the show-stopper with soft, clean carpet, very large primary bedroom with dual closets and  new white sliding barn door leading to beautiful NEW ceramic tile bathroom finished with  white & gray tones. Two additional guest rooms AND UPPER LEVEL LAUNDRY AREA  complete the bedroom level.  Lower level with plenty of natural light, half bath, vinyl flooring, and exit to rear fenced yard offer many living options as needs change.  Pride of ownership at every turn.  If you are looking for easy maintenance in a really fun spot at a great price, this is the one!  Professional photos coming after the snow!   Open House Saturday 1/27/24....12:30 - 2:30.  Ask for John
